[    39] By: abeltje                          on 2003-09-10 20:35:27 +0200
        Log: * [CHANGE] *big*
	       + allmost rewrite checksite:
		 + --save switch allows for the data to be stored
		 + --load switch allows to build a new (different) report
		     from saved data
